title: Cambridge Analytica files for bankruptcy in U.S.
text:
Cambridge Analytica files for bankruptcy in U.S. 1:31pm BST - 01:18
Cambridge Analytica, the political consultancy at the center of Facebook Inc's privacy scandal, filed for Chapter 7 bankruptcy in the United States late on Thursday. Jacob Greaves reports. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
